						               													<description>Is card game from the world of mafia. Each player is trying to reach the significant part of the most powerful people in the city. Be the first who control at least four of them and the city &amp;quot;victory&amp;quot; is yours.&amp;#10;Cards are divided in 3 categories&amp;#10;- Intriguer - necessary for activation of sentences&amp;#10;- Intrigue card - most in game - have 4 different meanings&amp;#10;1 - for composing of sentences (intrigues)&amp;#10;2 - symbol in right corner - sentences from cards with same symbol gives you additional advantage&amp;#10;3 - represent money&amp;#10;4 - can be played as single card&amp;#10;- Cards of powerful people in city (provost, taxi driver, pilot, murder, thief, ....)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game is based on drawing a cards from witch you compose the sentences (each card contain part of the sentence), Longer sentences allow you to make more complex and powerful actions.&amp;#10;In each turn, you can just draw one card, and play one card.&amp;#10;Other advantages depend on composed sentences (intrigues).&amp;#10;Rules of the game are quit simple and in fact almost everything is allowed, so also depends on you how you are able to control and make deals with other players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Simply - Fast and funny party game&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
